Welsh AM yana jin haushi don Y a matsayin wasa
Akwai damuwa a cikin wasu AMs don tattaunawa cewa ya kamata a canza sunayensu zuwa MWPs (Members of the Welsh Parliament).
Ya fara ne saboda shirin canza sunan ƙungiyar zuwa Majalisar Welsh.
AMs a duk bangarorin siyasa suna da damuwa cewa zai iya haifar da zargi.
Wani jam'iyyar AM ta Labour ta ce 'yan jam'iyyarta na damuwa cewa jam'iyyar ta fadi kamar Twp da Pwp.
Ga masu karatu a waje da Wales: A cikin Welsh twp yana nufin ɓarna, pwp yana nufin ɓarna.
AM mai saka Fursunoni ya ce wannan ya yi kama da duka da fushi, cewa yana da wasu abubuwa da ya kwatanta.
Wani dan majalisa na Welsh Conservative ya ce jam'iyyarsa "tuni ta bude baki" game da canjin sunan, amma ya ce wannan gajeriyar hanyar ne daga MWP zuwa Wasanni.
A wannan fahimtar, ana furta w na Welsh kamar yadda ake furta u na Turanci na Yorkshire.
Kwamitin Majalisar Dinkin Duniya, wanda ke tsara dokokin da za su kawo canjin sunan, ya ce: Dokar karshe da duk wani bayani da ake kira 'Yan Majalisar Dinkin Duniya zai kasance batun membobin kansu.
Gwamnatin Wales ta 2017 ta ba da izinin majalisa ta Welsh don canza sunansa.
A watan Yuni, Hukumar ta wallafa sakamakon shawarwarin jama'a da manufofin da suka gano goyon baya mai yawa don kiran taron kasa na Majalisar Welsh.
Game da sunan AM, Hukumar ta dogara ne akan 'yan majalisa na Welsh ko WMP, amma zaɓin MWP ya sami goyon baya mafi yawa daga shawarwarin jama'a.
AM ta ba da shawarar wasu zaɓuɓɓuka, amma gwagwarmayar cimma yarjejeniya na iya zama babban ciwo ga Babban Jami'in, Elin Jones, wanda ake tsammanin zai gabatar da takaddun shaida game da canje-canjen a cikin makonni masu zuwa.
Dokokin da aka yi wa gyare-gyare za su hada da wasu canje-canje a yadda majalisar dokokin kasar ke aiki, gami da dokokin da za a yi wa 'yan majalisar wakilai da kuma fasahar tsarin kungiyar.
'Yan majalisar wakilai za su yi zabe na karshe kan batun abin da za a kira su bayan sun yi muhawara kan dokar.
