Tsunami da Girgizar Kasa a Indonesia Sun Halaka Tsibiri, Sun Kashe Mutane da Yawa
Bayan girgizar kasa ta Lombok, alal misali, an gaya wa 'yan majalisar dattijai cewa ba gwamnati ba ce kuma ba a son su.
Ko da yake an kori fiye da kashi 10 cikin 100 na mutanen Lombok daga gidajensu, ba a sanar da wani bala'i na kasa da kasa ba, dalilin farko na neman taimakon kasashen waje.
A yawancin lokuta, da rashin alheri, sun bayyana a fili cewa ba sa bukatar taimakon kasashen waje, don haka yana da kalubale, in ji Mista Sumbung.
Tunda kungiyar Save the Children tana shirya tafiya zuwa Palu, ba a san ko ma'aikatan kasashen waje za su iya aiki a kasar ba.
Mista Sutopo, mai magana da yawun hukumar bala'i ta kasa, ya ce jami'an Indonesiya suna nazarin halin da ake ciki a Palu don ganin ko za a bar kamfanonin kasashen waje su taimaka wa kokarin bayar da agaji.
Domin girgizar kasa na Indonesia na faruwa a kai a kai, kasar ba ta shirya don fushin da ke faruwa ba.
An gina tashar tsaro ta tsunami a Aceh, amma ba a san ta a sauran yankuna ba.
Idan ba a yi gargadin tsunami a Palu ba, ko da an yi gargadin, hakan zai iya jawo mutuwar mutane.
A lokacin da ya fi dacewa, tafiya tsakanin tsibiran Indonesiya yana da wuya.
Bala'i na ƙasar yana ƙara kawo matsala.
Jirgin ruwan asibiti da aka ajiye a Lombok don kula da wadanda girgizar kasa ta shafa yanzu yana kan hanyarsa zuwa Palu, amma zai dauki akalla kwanaki uku kafin ya isa wurin da sabon bala'in ya auku.
Shugaba Joko Widodo ya yi watsi da batun inganta kayayyakin more rayuwa na Indonesia a yakin neman zabensa, amma ya kashe kudi a kan hanyoyi da hanyoyin jirgin kasa.
Amma rashin kudi da kuma kashe gwamnatin Mista Joko yayin da yake jiran sake zaben shekara mai zuwa.
Mista Joko ya kuma matsa lamba kan rikicin yanki da ke faruwa a Indonesia, inda 'yan asalin Musulmi suka karɓi tsarin addini.
An kashe mutane fiye da 1,000 kuma an kori dubban dubban mutane daga gidajensu a matsayin masu aikata laifuka na Krista da Musulmai a cikin yakin basasa, tare da wuka, baka da mashi, da sauran makamai masu linzami.
Kalli: Yadda Liverpool ta yi da Daniel Sturridge a wasan karshe na kakar wasa da Chelsea
Daniel Sturridge ya ceci Liverpool daga Premier League da Chelsea ta hanyar zura kwallo a minti na 89 a ranar Asabar a Stamford Bridge a London.
Sturridge ya samu wata wucewa daga hannun Xherdan Shaqiri a raga 30 a waje da Chelsea yayin da tawagarsa ke ci 1-0.
Ya sanya kwallon a hannun hagu kafin ya harba shi a saman gidan.
Jarabawar ta hau kan akwatin yayin da take tafiya a saman dama na raga.
Daga bisani kwallon ta wuce Kepa Arrizabalaga da hannu kuma ta fada cikin raga.
Yin kokarin shiga cikin yanayin, kama kwallon da 'yan wasa kamar Shaq da tserensa a duk lokacin da suke da karfi, don haka ni kaina na yi kokarin fitar da kaina yadda na fi karfi, Sturridge ya fada wa LiverpoolFC.com.
Na ga Kante yana zuwa, na taɓa shi sau ɗaya, ban yi tunani sosai ba, na harbe shi nan da nan.
Chelsea ta ci gaba da 1-0 a lokacin da aka dakatar da wasan bayan da Eden Hazard na Belgium ya ci kwallo a minti na 25.
Dan wasan Blues ya ba Mateo Kovacic wata hanya ta baya a wasan, kafin ya gudu zuwa filin wasa kuma ya buga wa Liverpool.
Kovacic ya yi wasan tsere a tsakiyar filin wasa.
Ya buga kwallo mai kyau, wanda ya kai Hazard cikin akwatin.
Hazard ya tsallake raga kuma ya buga kwallo a raga ta hanyar buga kwallo da kafar hagu kuma ya wuce Alisson Becker na Liverpool.
