Chelsea tana jiran Videoton a gasar cin kofin Europa ta UEFA da karfe 3 na yamma a ranar Alhamis a Landan.
Mutane 832 sun mutu a tsunami da ya auku a Indonesia
Adadin wadanda suka mutu a girgizar kasa da tsunami na Indonesia ya kai 832, in ji hukumar bala'i ta kasar da sanyin safiyar Lahadi.
An ce mutane da dama sun makale a karkashin gidajen da suka rushe sakamakon girgizar kasa mai karfin awo 7.5 da ta afku a ranar Juma'a da ta haifar da iska mai karfin kafa 20, mai magana da yawun kamfanin Sutopo Purwo Nugroho ya fadawa taron manema labarai.
Birnin Palu, da ke da mutane fiye da 380,000, ya cika da tarkace da ke tattare da gidajen da suka rushe.
'Yan sanda sun kama wani mutum, mai shekaru 32, a cikin binciken kisan kai yayin da yake yiwa wata mata wuka
An fara binciken kisan kai bayan da aka gano gawar wata mata a Birkenhard, Merseyside a safiyar yau.
An gano mutumin mai shekaru 44 da 7:55 na safe tare da raunukan wuka a Grayson Mews da John Road, an kama wani mutum mai shekaru 32 a cikin binciken kisan kai.
'Yan sanda suna kiran mutanen da ke yankin su zo su yi magana idan sun ga ko kuma sun ji wani abu.
Jami'in 'yan sanda Brian O'Hagan ya ce: "Binciken yana kan mataki na farko amma ina kira ga duk wanda ke cikin sansanin John Road a Birkenhead wanda ya ga ko ya ji wani abu mai ban mamaki ya tuntube mu.
Ina so in nemi kowa, musamman direbobi na taksi, wanda zai iya kama duk wani abu a cikin dashcam don tuntuɓar mu saboda suna iya samun bayanai masu mahimmanci don bincikenmu.
Wani mai magana da yawun 'yan sanda ya tabbatar da cewa matar da aka gano ta kasance daga Birkenhead, an same ta a cikin wani banki.
A wannan rana abokai sun yarda cewa su da matar sun zo sansanin don su tambayi inda aka same ta a safiyar yau.
Yanzu ana bincike kuma 'yan sanda sun ce suna shirye su gaya wa mataimakin wanda abin ya faru.
Wani direban tasi a Grayson Mew ya yi kokarin shiga gidan amma 'yan sanda sun gaya masa cewa babu wanda ke shiga ko fita daga gidan.
