Mutane sama da miliyan 20 ne suka kalli jawabin Brett Kavanaugh
Mutane sama da miliyan 20 ne suka kalli shaidar da aka bayar a ranar Alhamis daga Brett Kavanaugh wanda aka zaba a Kotun Koli da kuma wata mata da aka zargi da fyade a shekarar 1980, Christine Blasey Ford, a gidan talabijin.
Yanzu da aka ci gaba da yin zanga-zanga, kafofin yada labarai sun katse shirye-shiryen da ya kamata a yi a ranar Juma'a: yarjejeniyar da Sanata Jeff Flake na Arizona ya shirya don FBI ta gudanar da bincike na mako guda kan zargin.
Ford ya shaida wa Majalisar Dokokin cewa ya tabbata cewa Kavanaugh ya yi shaye-shaye kuma ya yi ƙoƙari ya cire rigarsa a wani bikin makarantar sakandare.
Kavanaugh, a cikin wata sanarwa mai ma'ana, ya ce ya tabbata kashi 100 bisa 100 cewa bai yi hakan ba.
Akwai yiwuwar cewa sama da mutane miliyan 20.4 ne Nielsen ya ce a ranar Juma'a suka kalli shi.
Kamfanin ya ƙidaya matsakaicin ra'ayi a CBS, ABC, NBC, CNN, Fox News Channel da MSNBC.
Ba a samu adadin lambobin da aka nuna a wasu tashoshin ba, ciki har da PBS, C-SPAN da Fox Business Network.
Amma Nielsen yana da matsala da yawan kallon mutane a tashar su.
Don a kwatanta, wannan ya yi daidai da yawan masu kallo a filin wasan ƙwallon ƙafa ko kuma a bikin ba da lambar yabo ta Academy.
Tashar Fox News, wacce masu gyara masu hankali suka goyi bayan nadin Kavanaugh, ta zarce dukkan cibiyoyin sadarwa ta hanyar samun matsakaicin adadin masu kallo miliyan 5.69 a duk tsawon lokacin da aka yi ta, in ji Nielsen.
ABC ta kasance ta biyu tare da masu kallo miliyan 3.26.
CBS tana da masu kallo miliyan 3.1, NBC tana da masu kallo miliyan 2.94, MSNBC tana da masu kallo miliyan 2.89 kuma CNN tana da masu kallo miliyan 2.52, in ji Nielsen.
Sa'ad da aka kammala tattaunawar, mutane sun soma son saƙon.
Flake ne mai kula da batun ranar Juma'a.
Kamar yadda wata kafar yada labarai ta Republican ta fitar da sanarwar cewa za ta goyi bayan Kavanaugh, kyamarorin CNN da CBS sun kama shi a safiyar ranar Juma'a tare da masu zanga-zangar da suka fusata da kuma nuna rashin amincewa da shi yayin da yake kokarin shiga cikin na'urar da ke kan hanyar zuwa da kuma daga majalisar zartarwa.
