Lee, wanda littafinsa AI Superpowers: China, Silicon Valley and the New World Order wanda Houghton Mifflin Harcourt ya wallafa a wannan watan, shi ne Shugaba na Sinovation Ventures, wanda ya zuba jari a kamfanin Face++, wanda ya fi shahara a kasar Sin.
A 1980 a Jami'ar Carnegie Mellon ya yi aiki a kan tsarin AI wanda ya ci nasara da mafi kyawun mawaƙa Othello a Amurka, daga baya ya zama shugaban zartarwa a Microsoft Research kuma shugaban sashen Google a China.
Lee ya yi imanin cewa gasar fasaha ta gwamnatin Amurka kamar Hukumar Kula da Ayyukan Nazarin Harkokin Tsaro ta Defense Advanced Research Projects Agency ta Robotics Challenge kuma ta tambayi lokacin da za a yi na gaba, don taimakawa wajen gano sababbin masu fafatawa.
