'Yan Macedonia sun kada kuri'ar neman sauya sunan kasarsu
'Yan Macedonia sun kada kuri'ar zaben ranar Lahadi kan sauya sunan kasar zuwa Jamhuriyar Arewacin Macedonia, don warware rikicin da ya shafe shekaru tsakanin Girka da ta hana ta shiga Tarayyar Turai da NATO.
Girka, wacce ke da yankin Macedonia, tana dagewa kan cewa sunan makwabciyarta yana cikin sunan da ke nuna da'awar yankin, kuma ta hana shi shiga NATO da EU.
Gwamnonin biyu sun cimma yarjejeniya a watan Yuni bisa ga sabon sunan da aka kwatanta, amma abokan adawar sun kasance manyan jihohi kuma sun yi jayayya cewa canjin zai lalata asalin kabilanci na yawancin Slavic na Macedonia.
Shugaban kasar Gjorge Ivanov ya ce ba zai yi takara ba, kuma kafofin yada labarai sun sake yin shakkar ko za a samu kashi 50 cikin dari da ake bukata domin zaben ya zama mai inganci.
Tambayar da aka yi a takardar zaben ta ce: Shin kun amince da shiga NATO da EU ta hanyar amincewa da yarjejeniyar da aka kulla da Girka?
Masu goyon bayan sauya sunan, ciki har da Firayim Minista Zoran Zaev, sun yi jayayya cewa farashin da ya kamata a biya shi ne bin bin bin tsarin EU da NATO ga Macedonia, daya daga cikin ƙasashe masu tasowa daga faduwar Yugoslavia.
Na zo yau ne domin in yi zabe domin makomar kasarmu, don matasa a Macedonia su iya rayuwa yadda suke so a karkashin kulawar Tarayyar Turai saboda hakan na nufin rayuwa mafi kyau ga dukkanmu, in ji Olivera Georgijevska, 79, a Skopje.
Duk da rashin bin doka, mambobin majalisar dokoki sun ce za su mutunta sakamakon zaben don tabbatar da muhimmancinsa.
Canjin sunan zai bukaci kashi biyu bisa uku na babban majalisa.
Hukumar zaben jihar ta ce ba a samu rahoton aikata laifi ba a karfe 1 na rana.
Koyaya, yawan masu jefa kuri'a ya kai kashi 16 cikin ɗari, idan aka kwatanta da kashi 34 cikin ɗari a zaɓen majalisar dokoki na baya a 2016 lokacin da kashi 66 cikin ɗari na masu jefa ƙuri'a suka ba da takardun zaɓen su.
"Na zabi na yi wa 'ya'yana murna, matsayinmu a Turai ne", in ji Gjose Tanevski, 62, wanda ya yi zaben shugaban kasa, Skopje.
Firayim Ministan Macedonia Zoran Zaev, matarsa Zorica da dansa Dushko sun gabatar da kuri'unsu na zaben a Macedonia don canza sunan kasar wanda zai bude hanya don shiga NATO da Tarayyar Turai a Strumica, Macedonia Satumba 30, 2018.
Shugaban majalisar dokokin Skopje, Vladimir Kavardarkov, 54, yana shirya karamin dandamali, yana gabatar da kujerar da ke gaban gidan wasan kwaikwayo wanda masu son hana zaben suka kafa.
Mun goyi bayan NATO da EU, amma muna son shiga ta hanyar tsaunuka, ba ta hanyar aiki ba Kavadarkov ya ce.
