Lebron zai fara buga wa Lakers wasa a ranar Lahadi a San Diego
An kusan kammala wasan ne domin magoya baya da ke jiran ganin LeBron James ya fara bugawa Los Angeles Lakers wasa.
Shugaban Lakers Luke Walton ya ce James zai shiga wasan neman gurbin a ranar Lahadi tsakanin Denver Nuggets da San Diego.
Amma ba a san tsawon lokacin da zai yi a wasan ba.
Ya kamata ya fi ɗaya amma bai kai 48, wanda Walton ya ce shafin yanar gizon Lakers daidai ne.
Mai ba da rahoto game da Lakers Mike Trudell ya rubuta cewa James na iya buga wasanni kaɗan.
Bayan kammala aikin a farkon wannan makon, an tambayi James game da shirinsa na shirin shekara ta shida na Lakers.
"Ba na son wasan da ake yi a farkon lokacin da nake aiki a yanzu, don shirya", in ji shi.
A lokacin taron Trump na West Virginia.
Shugaba Donald Trump ya fara taron siyasa da yawa a Wheeling, West Virginia.
Wannan shi ne karo na farko na taron siyasa guda biyar da Trump zai yi a cikin makonni biyar masu zuwa, tare da tsayawa a cikin abokan tarayya da Tennessee da Mississippi.
Da yake yana da zaɓen da ya fi dacewa don neman takararsa a Kotun Koli, Trump yana fatan ya ƙarfafa goyon baya ga zaben da ke tafe, yayin da 'yan Republican ke fuskantar barazanar rasa iko da majalisar dokoki lokacin da aka sanya hannu a watan Nuwamba.
A wane lokaci ne za a yi zaben shugaban kasa na yammacin Virginia a daren yau, kuma ta yaya za ka iya kallon shi a yanar gizo?
An shirya taron Trump na Wheeling West Virginia a karfe 7 na dare ET, Asabar, 29 ga Satumba, 2018.
Kuna iya kallon taron Trump na West Virginia a kan layi, a ƙasa daga bidiyo kai tsaye akan Youtube.
Trump na iya magana ne game da muhawarar wannan makon game da dan takarar Kotun Koli Brett Kavanaugh, wanda ya yi taɓarɓarewar zargi game da zargin jima'i da kuma ƙuri'ar da ake tsammani ta Majalisar Dattijai ta tsaya har tsawon mako guda yayin da FBI ke bincike.
Amma babban manufar jam'iyyun siyasa da yawa shine taimakawa Jam'iyyar Republican a cikin babban zaben Nuwamba kuma ta sami kwarin gwiwa.
Don haka, shugaban Trump ya ce za a yi zaben mako biyar na gaba don karfafa masu tallafawa da masu tallafawa, yayin da 'yan Republican ke kokarin karewa da fadada rashin amincewarsu a majalisa, a cewar Reuters.
Sarrafa majalisar dokoki yana da mahimmanci ga shirinsa, don haka shugaban zai yi aiki a cikin birane da yawa kamar yadda zai iya, yayin da muke shiga cikin siyasa wani mai magana da yawun siyasa na Trump wanda bai so a bayyana sunansa ya fada wa Reuters.
An shirya shi a gidan wasan kwaikwayo na Wesbanco Wheeling, taron siyasa na dare zai iya jawo magoya baya daga Ohio da Pennsylvania kuma ya sami rahoto daga kafofin watsa labarai na Pittsburgh, a cewar West Virginia Metro News.
A ranar Asabar ne Trump zai ziyarci West Virginia a karo na biyu a watan da ya gabata, jihar da ya yi nasara da kashi 40 cikin dari a shekarar 2016.
Trump yana kokarin taimaka wa dan takarar majalisar dokokin West Virginia Patrick Morrisey, wanda ke cikin bincike.
Ba alama ce mai kyau ba ga Morrisey cewa shugaban kasa zai zo ya inganta shi a cikin bincike, in ji Simon Haeder, masanin kimiyyar siyasa a Jami'ar West Virginia, a cewar Reuters.
