A al'adance, cutar kanjamau ta yadu cikin sauri a wasu sassan kasar Sin saboda cutar jini.
Amma adadin masu kamuwa da cutar HIV ta wannan hanyar ya ragu zuwa sifili, in ji jami'an lafiya na kasar Sin a wani taron da aka gudanar a lardin Yunnan.
Hakika, kowace shekara, adadin mutane da ke da cutar HIV da Cutar Kwayar cuta ta Ƙanjamau ya ƙaru da mutane 100,000.
Yaduwar cutar kanjamau ta hanyar jima'i lamari ne mai tsanani a cikin al'ummar LGBT na kasar Sin.
An soke cin zarafin jinsi a kasar Sin a shekarar 1997, amma har yanzu ana cin zarafin LGBT.
Saboda dokokin tsaro na al'umma, binciken bincike ya yi hasashen cewa kimanin kashi 70-90% na maza masu yin jima'i za su yi aure.
Yawancin cututtuka suna zuwa ne daga rashin yin isasshen kariya ta jima'i a cikin waɗannan abota.
Tun daga 2003, gwamnatin kasar Sin ta yi alkawarin samun maganin cutar kanjamau a matsayin wani bangare na kokarin magance matsalar.
