Washington na iya ko kuma ya zama dole ta yi amfani da Sojojin Ruwa na kasar don hana Rasha shiga kasuwanni, ciki har da Gabas ta Tsakiya, in ji US Secretary of State Ryan Zinke, kamar yadda Washington Examiner ta ruwaito.
Zinke ya yi zargin cewa shigar Rasha cikin Syria - sanannen, inda take aiki a kan kiran gwamnati mai adalci - wata dabara ce ta bincika sabon kasuwar makamashi.
"Na yi imanin dalilin da ya sa suke Gabas ta Tsakiya shi ne don su yi kasuwanci kamar yadda suke yi a gabashin Turai, a kudancin Turai", in ji shi.
