Mata ba za su manta da abin da ya faru jiya ba - ba za su manta da gobe ba amma Nuwamba,  Karine Jean-Pierre, babban mai ba da shawara da kuma mai magana da yawun al'umma don ci gaban MoveOn ya ce a ranar Juma'a, a cewar jaridar Washington, D.C.
A safiyar ranar Juma'a, masu zanga-zangar sun yi ikirarin cewa Nuwamba tana zuwa! yayin da suke zanga-zangar a cikin hanyar Majalisar Dokoki yayin da 'yan Republican suka yi amfani da Majalisar Shari'a don zaɓar ci gaba da zaɓen Kavanaugh duk da sanarwar Dr. Christine Blasey Ford, Mic ya bayyana.
"Kishin da kuma himmar 'yan Democrat zai zama na musamman", in ji Stu Rothenberg, wani mai nazarin siyasa wanda ba shi da wata alaka da shi.
