Tun kafin a sanar da Ford cewa ya yi zargin cewa yana da lalata da dan takarar Kotun Koli, masu bincike sun yi tunanin cewa za a iya samun mummunan sakamako idan 'yan Republican suka ci gaba da goyon baya.
Wannan ya zama rikici ga GOP, Michael Steele, tsohon shugaban jam'iyyar Republican Party, ya fada a farkon makon da ya gabata, a cewar NBC News.
Ba wai kawai game da zaben majalisa ba ko kuma game da zaben karshe ko kuma ko an nada Kavanaugh, amma game da yadda 'yan Republican suka gudanar da wannan kuma yadda suka amsa, Guy Cecil, shugaban fifiko na Amurka, wani rukuni na taimakawa wajen zaben' yan Democrat, ya nuna wa manema labarai.
