Wani sabon bincike daga YouGov ya nuna cewa kashi 41 cikin ɗari na waɗanda aka yi wa binciken sun yarda ko kuma sun yarda da abin da Ford ya faɗa, yayin da kashi 35 cikin ɗari suka ce sun yarda ko kuma sun yarda da Kavanaugh.
Bugu da ƙari, kashi 38 cikin ɗari sun ce suna ganin Kavanaugh ya ƙi ko ya ƙi shi a lokacin da ya yi ikirarin, yayin da kashi 30 cikin ɗari suka ce haka ma Ford.
Bayan Flake ya yi gargadi, FBI yanzu tana binciken zargin da Ford ya yi, tare da akalla wani mai zargin, Deborah Ramirez, The Guardian ta ruwaito.
Ford ya yi ikirarin a gaban majalisar dokoki a karkashin rantsuwa a makon da ya gabata cewa Kavanaugh ya sha giya a lokacin da yake da shekaru 17.
