Girgizar ƙasa da tsunami a ƙasar Indonesia
Akalla mutane 384 ne suka mutu a lokacin da wata girgizar kasa da tsunami suka afku a birnin Palu na Indonesia a ranar Juma'a, in ji jami'ai, suna sa ran adadin wadanda suka mutu zai karu.
Bayan da aka bude hanyoyin sadarwa, jami'an agaji ba su samu wani bayani daga yankin Donggala ba, yankin dutse na Palu kusa da cibiyar girgizar kasa mai karfin 7.5.
A Palu, mutane fiye da 16,000 sun bar gidajensu.
Ga wasu bayanai game da Palu da Donggala, a tsibirin Sulawesi:
Palau babban birni ne na yankin Tsakiyar Sulawesi, wanda ke ƙarshen bakin teku a yammacin tsibirin Sulawesi, yana da yawan jama'a 379,800 a shekarar 2017.
Birnin yana bikin cika shekaru 40 da girgizar ƙasa da tsunami suka auku.
Donggala yanki ne mai tsawon kilomita 300 (mil 180) a yammacin arewacin tsibirin Sulawesi.
Ƙasar ta, yanki ne na gudanarwa a ƙarƙashin sansanin, yana da ƙididdigar yawan mutane 299,200 a 2017.
Kamfanin kamun kifi da noma sune manyan ayyukan tattalin arzikin yankin Tsakiyar Sulawesi, musamman yankin Donggala.
Har ila yau, nickel yana da mahimmanci a sansanin, amma ya fi girma a Morowali, da kuma kariya ta fuskar Sulawesi.
Tsunami ya afku a Palu da Dongalla sau da yawa a cikin shekaru 100 da suka gabata, in ji Hukumar Kula da Bala'i ta Indonesia.
A shekara ta 1938, tsunami ya kashe mutane fiye da 200 kuma ya lalata ɗarurruwan gidaje a Donggala.
Wani tsunami kuma ya auku a yammacin Donggala a shekara ta 1996, ya kashe mutane tara.
Indonesia tana cikin yankin da ake yawan girgizar ƙasa da kuma ƙanƙara.
Ga wasu manyan girgizar ƙasa da tsunami a cikin 'yan shekarun nan:
2004: Girgizar kasa mai karfin gaske a gabar yammacin yankin Aceh da ke arewacin Sumatra a Indonesiya a ranar 26 ga Disamba ta haifar da tsunami wanda ya afkawa garuruwa 14, ya kashe mutane 226,000 a gabar tekun Tekun Indiya, fiye da rabin su a Aceh.
2005: Wani girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfi ya afku a gabar yammacin Sumatra a ƙarshen Maris da farkon Afrilu.
Daruruwan mutane sun mutu a Tsibirin Nias, a bakin tekun Sumatra.
2006: Girgizar kasa mai karfin awo 6.8 ta afku a kudancin Java, tsibirin da ke da yawan jama'a a Indonesia, kuma tsunami ya afku a gabar teku ta kudu, inda ya kashe mutane 700.
2009: Girgizar kasa mai karfin awo 7.6 ta afku a kusa da garin Padang, babban birnin yankin Sumatra ta Yamma.
Mutane fiye da 1,100 ne suka mutu.
2010: Girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfin 7.5 ta afkawa tsibirin Mentawai, a bakin tekun Sumatra, kuma tsunami mai zurfin mita 10 ya lalata yankuna da yawa kuma ya kashe mutane 300.
2016: Wani karamin girgizar kasa ya afku a karamar hukumar Pidie Jaya a Aceh, wanda ya haifar da barna da rikici da kuma tsammanin mutane da yawa sun mutu sakamakon girgizar kasa da tsunami na 2004.
Babu wata tsunami da ta haifar a wannan lokacin, amma gidaje da suka rushe sun kashe mutane sama da 100.
2018: Girgizar kasa mai karfin gaske ta afkawa tsibirin Lombok na Indonesia, inda ta kashe mutane sama da 500, galibi a arewacin tsibirin.
Girgizar ta lalata gidaje dubbai kuma ta sa wasu matafiya cikin matsala na ɗan lokaci.
