Sabuntawar Ruwa: Yawan ruwa ya ragu a Pinellas, Manatee da Sarasota
Rahoton da aka samu daga Hukumar Kifi da Dabbobin daji ta Florida ya nuna raguwar yawan ruwan da ke shigowa cikin yankin Tampa Bay.
Ta hanyar FWC, an ba da rahoton yanayin fure-fure a cikin ƙananan yankunan Pinellas, Manatee, Sarasota, Charlotte da Collies - wanda ke haifar da raguwa da raguwa.
Ƙarƙashin ruwan yana da nisan mil 130 daga bakin tudu na Pinellas zuwa kudancin ƙaramin garin Lee.
Ana iya ganin raƙuman ruwa a cikin nisan mil 10 na kogin Hillsborough County, amma a cikin ƙananan wurare a cikin makon da ya gabata.
An kuma gano ruwan zuma a gundumar Pasco.
An yi kusan rabin ruwa a cikin ko a bakin tekun Pinellas Country a makon da ya gabata, ƙananan ruwa zuwa babban ruwa a cikin Hillsborough County, ƙananan ruwa zuwa babban ruwa a cikin Manatee County, ƙananan ruwa zuwa babban ruwa a cikin ko a bakin tekun Sarasota County, ƙananan ruwa zuwa rabin ruwa a cikin Charlotte County, ƙananan ruwa zuwa babban ruwa a cikin ko a bakin tekun Lee County, da ƙananan ruwa a cikin Collier County.
Har ila ana samun rahotanni game da cin zarafin mata a Pinellas, Manatee, Sarasota, Lee, da Collier.
An samu ciwon numfashi a arewacin Florida da yammacin jihar a makon da ya gabata.
